Game
====

Menu
----
Before the game actually starts all players choose what "ability"
they want to have and what weaponry they buy. Weapons' prices and damage
is set in 'weapons.conf' file in directory where server binary is run,
the similar goes with abilites.

Host menu consists of:
*ability choice
*number of bought weapons (note: you cannot 'sell' weapons you bought earlier,
                           but you can change the order)
*wind (on|off, random every {shoot, turn})

Client menu consists of:
*ability choice
*number of bought weapons

Gameplay
--------
Each tank can shoot or use ability every turn.
Only one tank shoots at the time.

Victory
-------
The winner is the tank that stays last alive.
In other words, all other tanks are destroyed.
